### Configuration

You can configure this plugin in `.arere/settings.json`:

```json
{
  "plugins": {
    "{{pluginName}}": {
      "enabled": true,
      "config": {
        "greeting": "Hello",
        "enabled": true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

